Ing '''Sansha''' metung yang prefecture king lalawigan ning [[Hainan]], [[Maldang Republika ning Tsina]] a manibala (king tutu o king lagyu) kareng mapilang grupu da reng isla king [[South China Sea]], kayabe la reng [[Spratly Islands|Spratly]] ampong [[Paracel Islands]] at saka ing  [[Macclesfield Bank]].<ref name="SanshaRectified">{{cite web|url=http://english.sina.com/china/2012/0621/479131.html|title=China sets up Sansha City to administer South China Sea islands|publisher=[[Sina]]|date=June 21, 2012|accessdate=June 21, 2012}}</ref> Pipapapaten de ing kabilugan ning teritoryu, at myayaliwa ing kabilyan ning ''[[de facto]]'' ning Tsina king lugal. Maki kabilyan yang administratibu ing Sansha katumbas ning [[lakanbalen a kadaneng prefecture]] (''prefecture-level city''), at melalang ya anyang 24 Julio 2012.<ref name="xinhuaen0" />

